items.title: Awesome Cli Apps
items.content_text:
### Utilities / Shell Utilities

*   [has (⭐725)](https://github.com/kdabir/has) - Checks for the presence of various commands and their versions on the path.
*   [Ultimate Plumber (⭐8.5k)](https://github.com/akavel/up) - Write Linux pipes with live previews.
*   [fkill-cli (⭐6.9k)](https://github.com/sindresorhus/fkill-cli) - Simple cross-platform process killer.
*   [undollar (⭐190)](https://github.com/ImFeelingDucky/undollar) - Strip the '$' preceding copy-pasted terminal commands.
*   [pipe\_exec (⭐73)](https://github.com/koraa/pipe_exec) - Run executables from stdin, pipes and ttys without creating a temporary file.
items.content_html:
